![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/433ee000-9d83-44dd-865d-5481097ce744/FB_IMG_1712551250315.jpg?format=original)

## **WWE RAW RESULTS 04-08-2024**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5ad7b444-ed27-4f14-94b6-91d54b4e4291/20240408_170353.jpg?format=original)

Paul “Triple H” Levesque opens WWE RAW. He receives a standing ovation and “Thank You, Hunter” chants.

Triple H thanks the WWE Universe and says WrestleMania XL was the biggest WrestleMania of all time by any metrics.

Triple H kicks off the new era by introducing Cody Rhodes

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0d3a278c-1d80-4e40-8af3-e77457ba94f2/20240408_170909.jpg?format=original)

Cody Rhodes is out to a massive reaction. You deserve it chants break out. Triple H says Cody does deserve it and then they play a really nice video that brings Cody to tears

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/93f74ec1-88a5-455a-938b-0bf9d310e3c1/20240408_171745.jpg?format=original)

Cody Rhodes asks Samantha to introduce him again again and she does. “UNDISPUTED WWE CHAMPION”. Universal, no more.

Cody leads a Thank You, Roman. Plays a video of his daughter saying he’s finished the story.

Ladies and gentlemen, my name is Cody Rhodes. Once undesirable, then undeniable. Now WWE Undisputed Champion.

Cody is gonna leave when he's interrupted by the Rock

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c5fe8cde-63ae-47d4-bf8f-672bbc135a85/20240408_172608.jpg?format=original)

The audience gives Dwayne insane heat that has to be censored multiple times. The Rock finally starts talking sarcastically gives Cody Rhodes a bunch of backhanded compliments.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2f25e7a3-4e87-4746-ac0e-88c798725889/20240408_173418.jpg?format=original)

The Rock asks Cody to swap belts with him. The Rock gives the belt back and says he has to go away now. Back to Hollywood.

But when he comes back, he's coming for Cody.

## **_“Your story with Roman Reigns is over. But our story has just begun.”_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/11db3c37-b471-4c17-a41d-76c7627c08ee/20240408_174037.jpg?format=original)

Cody calls himself the People's Champion. The Rock says he has one more thing to give Cody. He hands Cody a mystery item and asks Cody never to break his heart again.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3ce50495-c229-4bdc-a494-525ede2ddff4/20240408_180516.jpg?format=original)

BREAKING: The WWE Draft will be taking place on the April 26th SmackDown & April 29th WWE RAW 

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/190e418d-7fa3-4dd6-a94d-1c88926d9bea/20240408_174939.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SURPRISE: ILJA DRAGUNOV VS SHINSUKE NAKAMURA_**
    

Pretty hard hitting but quick match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0b9b770f-68b2-41fa-9327-c480ee3d81fd/20240408_175458.jpg?format=original)

## **_WINNER: ILJA DRAGUNOV_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c5e40e09-d492-4363-af1d-af986044afa3/20240408_181052.jpg?format=original)

Judgement Day is out to show off their new dominance. Rhea and Damian both World Champions. R-Truth is still thinking he’s part of the group.

He offers to invite the Miz into the group. Miz is out, says he doesn’t want to be in the group.

JD wants a tag title match but Truth challenges Judgement Day to a six man tag. Awesome Truth and a “man we can’t see” against Judgement Day.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4ec948f4-43f7-4c8c-86ce-8f9e315b323f/20240408_182524.jpg?format=original)

1.  ## **_JUDGEMENT DAY VS AWESOME TRUTH AND A MAN WE CANT SEE AKA JOHN CENA!_**
    

Pretty nothing match until John Cena appears at the end and helps immediately end the match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f65e170b-9088-4eca-9680-bcafa3b75350/20240408_182730.jpg?format=original)

