*   ## **_SURPRISE: ROXANNE PEREZ VS INDI HARTWELL_**
    

Roxanne aggressively takes out Hartwell fairly quickly.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1102a81f-b338-4290-a4a0-cfd75d746176/20240408_184332.jpg?format=original)

## **_WINNER: ROXANNE PEREZ_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2ebdb954-6b0c-4afa-8f40-23652dbb7a20/20240408_184327.jpg?format=original)

Sami runs into an old friend before heading out for a promo

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b83d395a-6a28-4ccc-959a-52dea945baf8/20240408_185445.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn is thanking the audience when he’s interrupted by Imperium minus GUNTHER. They call him a bum. Chad Gable comes out to save Sami from a beat down and a tag match is set.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/03a41985-6c13-4f3d-9448-e03f8b3ff07d/20240408_190328.jpg?format=original)

