*   ## **_WINNER: JADE CARGILL_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/12833b6f-3ce4-4067-93ec-0d13bb0ad80e/processed_20240408_193119.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn vs Chad Gable for the Intercontinental Championship set for next week in Montreal!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8ae4e143-e55f-4afe-9696-dc8bda0ba0a5/20240408_193111.jpg?format=original)

Drew McIntyre calls Damian Priest “Bondage Undertaker” and says he would whip Damian's ass but he would probably like it.

Drew McIntyre says his World Championship dreams lasted 5 minutes but "5 mins is longer than most of you last in bed" to the crowd.

Finally it’s on sight for CM Punk when he returns. Then Jey Uso interrupts and its time for the main event

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cb908497-74ac-4700-9923-15b082f6fd65/20240408_194059.jpg?format=original)

WWE filmed a documentary of the Road to Wrestlemania XL. Looks like a good watch

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d512b3f9-c930-474d-a09d-02000540dd18/Screenshot_20240408_195726.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_NUMBER ONE CONTENDERS FATAL FOUR WAY: DREW MCINTYRE VS JEY USO VS RICOCHET VS BRONSON REED_**
    

Pretty excellent fatal four way. Drew and Bronson had a great section in the center of the match. And I did not expect CM Punk to cost Drew McIntyre another opportunity tonight at all.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/76c8b63f-501c-451c-9d76-1d43e0d428c6/20240408_200256.jpg?format=original)

## **_WINNER AND NEW #1 CONTENDER FOR THE WWE WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP: JEY USO_**

